      "text": "A key word of Robin’s referred to this:*formacion*. Formacion implies the cultivating of capability - or as we also call it here, **labour power** - at scale, in a complex and potentially beautiful ‘dance of knowing’ whose scope embraces *skilful knowing, visioning, communicating, organising, apprehending, cultivating, assembling, making and remaking*. \n"
