      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "e8bcda5bdce18427",
      "text": "The unfamiliar term *formacion* points to an underdeveloped but pivotal practice of the **forming of formations** - skilfully producing and orchestrating well-understood, well-founded, well-organised, well-oriented formations of activist practice, at scale, with scope, in the course of the everyday living and working of ‘ordinary working people’. \n"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
